                                <scriptNote>The ink is either tannin ink or an
                                    iron gall ink; however, to take a final decision on the sort of ink
                                    an instrumental analysis is preferable (see the spectroscopical
                                    analysis of 2011).</scriptNote>
                            </scriptDesc>
